        <h3><a href="../comment/9689#comment-9689" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">Some systems may have a</a></h3>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Some systems may have a sensible-editor alias - probably all the Debian-based ones: <a href="http://www.tin.org/bin/man.cgi?section=1&amp;topic=sensible-editor">http://www.tin.org/bin/man.cgi?section=1&amp;topic=sensible-editor</a></p>
<p>There's also the EDITOR environment variable:<br />
<a href="http://www.tin.org/bin/man.cgi?section=7&amp;topic=environ">http://www.tin.org/bin/man.cgi?section=7&amp;topic=environ</a></p>
</div></div></div>          </div>
